QuestData.Title: Create Your Own Strength
QuestData.Description:
For something that has been sitting on the ocean floor, there is still power to be found in this item.
Take your piece of Benthic armor to Voidbinder Zorlan. He has been eyeing it with great curiosity.
Go ahead and humor the ethereal and let him have a look.
Maybe he has something to offer.
QuestData.LogDescription: Upgrade a piece of Benthic armor through Voidbinder Zorlan.

Objectives.Objective: Upgrade a piece of Benthic Armor
Identify a piece of Benthic Armor
